            </div>

            <div class="thread-content">
                <!-- Original Message -->
                <div class="original-message">
                    <img src="images/user1-avatar.jpg" alt="User" class="message-avatar">
                    <div class="message-content">
                        <div class="message-header">
                            <span class="message-author">AliceGamer</span>
                            <span class="message-timestamp">Today at 2:47 PM</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="message-text">
                            Hey everyone! Just finished the new God of War game. What an incredible experience! Anyone else played it yet?
